    <description>When a contact is linked to several accounts (multi-site setup), the automation should create a direct relationship with the account where the SaaS Onboarding Stage in the Combined Funnel is the most advanced. If an account reaches the &quot;Activated&quot; status in its SaaS Onboarding stage, we then shift that contact&apos;s direct association to another linked account that is the furthest along in the Onboarding Funnel Stage.

If the account that reached the &quot;Activated&quot; status also has other contacts associated with it and is flagged as &quot;Onboarding SaaS Primary Contact&quot;, we should move these contacts to the other account that is the furthest along in the Onboarding Funnel Stage.
6/26/24 - BW - Updated to drive off of new Funnel fields on School Object</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>forContactId15Char</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>LEFT({!Get_Newly_Updated_SaaS_Contact.Id},15)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>forDirectSaaSFunnelLevel</name>
        <dataType>Number</dataType>
        <expression>IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Entering SaaS Funnel&apos;, 1,
  IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Uploading Students&apos;, 2,
    IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Adding Parents&apos;, 3,
      IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Logging First Activity&apos;, 4,
        IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Initiating Parent Signup&apos;, 5,
          IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Logging More Activities&apos;, 6,
            IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Increasing Parent Adoption&apos;, 7,
              IF({!Get_Direct_CF_Record.SaaS_Onboarding_Funnel_Stage__c} = &apos;Activated&apos;,8,0
              )
            )
          )
        )
      )
    )
  )
)</expression>
        <scale>0</scale>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
